Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, the finest bowling alley experience. My name is Jordan. How can I assist you today?

Hi Jordan, I'm having some issues with my billing statement.

I’d be happy to help you with that. Could I have your name, please?

Sure, my name is Alex Smith.

Thank you, Alex. To access your account, could you please provide me with your customer ID number?

Yes, my customer ID is two three nine zero seven.

Thanks, Alex. One more thing, could I verify the last four digits of the phone number associated with your account?

Sure, it’s eight seven six five.

Perfect, Alex. I’ve accessed your account and I see the issue with your billing. I will resolve this for you right away.

Thank you for your patience, Alex. The issue has been corrected. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

No, that was all. Thanks for your help!

You're welcome! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
